description: Premium over-ear headphones with active noise cancellation, 30-hour battery life, and premium sound quality. Features include quick charging, multi-device connectivity, and comfortable ear cushions for all-day wear. Perfect for travel, work, or leisure.

Extra thick 6mm yoga mat with non-slip texture on both sides. Made from eco-friendly TPE material, includes carrying strap. Ideal for yoga, pilates, stretching, and floor exercises. Easy to clean and maintain.

Insulated stainless steel water bottle keeps drinks cold for 24 hours or hot for 12 hours. BPA-free, leak-proof lid with carrying handle. Wide mouth for easy filling and cleaning. Available in multiple colors.

Advanced fitness tracker with heart rate monitor, sleep tracking, step counter, and GPS. Compatible with iOS and Android. Water-resistant up to 50m. Battery life up to 7 days. Includes multiple sport modes and smartphone notifications.
100% organic cotton t-shirt, soft and breathable. Pre-shrunk for perfect fit. Available in multiple colors and sizes (S-XXL). Made from sustainably sourced cotton. Machine washable.

Complete resistance band set with 5 different resistance levels. Includes door anchor, handles, and ankle straps. Portable and perfect for home workouts, physical therapy, or gym training. Comes with exercise guide.

Modern LED desk lamp with touch control and adjustable brightness. 3 color temperature modes (warm, neutral, cool). USB charging port built-in. Energy-efficient and eye-friendly lighting. Perfect for office or study.

Whey protein isolate with 25g protein per serving. Low carb, low sugar. Delicious chocolate flavor. Supports muscle recovery and growth. Third-party tested for quality. Mixes easily with water or milk.

Durable laptop backpack with padded compartment for 15.6 inch laptops. Multiple pockets for organization. Water-resistant material with reinforced stitching. Comfortable padded shoulder straps and back panel. USB charging port.

Programmable drip coffee maker with 12-cup capacity. Auto-brew feature with 24-hour timer. Pause-and-serve function. Permanent filter included. Keep-warm function up to 2 hours. Easy to clean removable parts.

Lightweight running shoes with responsive cushioning. Breathable mesh upper with reinforced toe cap. Durable rubber outsole for traction. Available in multiple sizes and colors. Suitable for road running and gym workouts.
Ergonomic wireless mouse with 2.4GHz connection. 6 programmable buttons and adjustable DPI (800-3200). Comfortable grip reduces wrist strain. Works with Windows and Mac. Battery life up to 18 months.
Pure essential oils set including lavender, peppermint, eucalyptus, tea tree, and more. 100% natural with no additives. Perfect for aromatherapy, diffusers, or DIY projects. Comes with usage guide.
Pre-seasoned cast iron skillet, 12-inch diameter. Even heat distribution for perfect cooking. Oven-safe up to 500°F. Compatible with all cooktops including induction. Comes with care instructions.

High-density foam roller for muscle recovery and myofascial release. Textured surface for deep tissue massage. 13-inch length, lightweight and portable. Helps reduce muscle soreness and improve flexibility.

Portable Bluetooth speaker with 360-degree sound. 12-hour battery life and IPX7 waterproof rating. Built-in microphone for hands-free calls. Compact design perfect for outdoor activities. Pairs with two devices simultaneously.

3-piece bamboo cutting board set in different sizes. Naturally antibacterial and eco-friendly. Knife-friendly surface won't dull blades. Easy to clean and maintain. Includes juice groove on largest board.
Adjustable dumbbell set, each dumbbell adjusts from 5-50 lbs. Space-saving design replaces 15 sets of weights. Quick-adjust mechanism with secure locking. Anti-roll design. Perfect for home gym.

HEPA air purifier removes 99.97% of particles. Covers rooms up to 300 sq ft. 3-stage filtration system. Quiet operation with sleep mode. Air quality indicator and auto mode. Filter replacement indicator.
Contoured memory foam pillow for neck and shoulder support. Hypoallergenic and dust mite resistant. Breathable bamboo cover, removable and washable. Ideal for side and back sleepers.
Digital kitchen scale with 11 lb capacity. Accurate to 0.1 oz/1g. Large LCD display and touch-sensitive buttons. Tare function and multiple unit conversions. Slim design with tempered glass platform.

Polarized sunglasses with UV400 protection. Lightweight frame with comfortable nose pads. Reduces glare and eye strain. Available in multiple styles and colors. Includes protective case and cleaning cloth.
Plant-based protein bars with 10g protein each. Organic ingredients, gluten-free and vegan. Low sugar, high fiber. Variety pack with 3 flavors. Perfect for pre/post workout or healthy snacking.

Mechanical gaming keyboard with RGB backlighting. Customizable per-key lighting effects. Tactile mechanical switches for precise typing. Anti-ghosting technology. Durable aluminum frame. Compatible with Windows and Mac.
Ceramic non-stick frying pan, 10-inch diameter. PFOA-free and toxin-free coating. Even heat distribution. Oven-safe up to 400°F. Dishwasher safe. Ergonomic handle stays cool during cooking.
Rechargeable electric toothbrush with 5 brushing modes. 2-minute timer with 30-second intervals. Pressure sensor protects gums. Up to 4 weeks battery life. Includes 3 brush heads and travel case.

High-density foam yoga blocks, 2-pack. Provides stability and support for various poses. Lightweight and durable. Non-slip surface with beveled edges. Easy to clean. Perfect for beginners and advanced practitioners.

Insulated lunch bag with leak-proof lining. Keeps food cold or hot for hours. Multiple compartments for organization. Adjustable shoulder strap. Easy to clean. Perfect for work, school, or outdoor activities.

Smart WiFi LED bulbs, works with Alexa and Google Home. Adjustable brightness and 16 million colors. Schedule and control from smartphone app. Energy-efficient and long-lasting (25,000 hours). Easy setup.

Mini resistance loop bands set with 5 different resistance levels. Perfect for glute activation, leg workouts, and physical therapy. Portable and durable. Non-slip design. Includes carrying bag and exercise guide.

Stainless steel mixing bowl set in 5 sizes (1.5 to 8 quarts). Nested design for space-saving storage. Non-slip bases and measurement marks. Dishwasher safe. Versatile for mixing, serving, and storage.
True wireless earbuds with active noise cancellation. 6-hour battery life plus 24 hours with charging case. IPX5 water resistance. Touch controls and voice assistant support. Quick charge feature.
Grass-fed collagen peptides powder, unflavored. Supports skin, hair, nails, and joint health. Easily dissolves in hot or cold liquids. 20g collagen per serving. Paleo and keto-friendly.

Portable double hammock with tree straps included. Supports up to 500 lbs. Lightweight and compact, packs into attached stuff sack. Breathable parachute nylon. Perfect for camping, backyard, or beach.

3-tier bamboo spice rack organizer. Expandable design fits different cabinet sizes. Holds up to 30 spice jars. Easy assembly. Natural bamboo construction. Keeps spices organized and easily accessible.
Extended gaming mouse pad, 36x12 inches. Smooth surface optimized for gaming mice. Non-slip rubber base. Stitched edges prevent fraying. Machine washable. Large enough for keyboard and mouse.
Adult multivitamin gummies with essential vitamins and minerals. Great-tasting fruit flavors. Gluten-free and gelatin-free. Supports immune health, energy, and overall wellness. 60-day supply.
Reusable shopping bags set of 6 in assorted colors. Each bag holds up to 50 lbs. Folds into attached pouch for easy storage. Machine washable. Eco-friendly alternative to plastic bags.

Digital air fryer with 5.8 quart capacity. 8 preset cooking programs. Temperature range 180-400°F. Non-stick basket and dishwasher safe parts. Recipes included. Healthier cooking with little to no oil.
Weighted jump rope with adjustable length. Comfortable foam handles with ball bearings for smooth rotation. Weighted rope improves cardio workout. Portable and durable. Includes spare cable.
USB-C to USB-A charging cables, 3-pack (6ft each). Fast charging and data sync. Durable braided nylon design. Compatible with most USB-C devices. Tangle-free. Lifetime warranty.
Green tea extract capsules with EGCG. Supports metabolism and energy. Powerful antioxidants. Non-GMO and vegan. 90-day supply. Third-party tested for purity and potency.
Over-the-sink dish drying rack, roll-up design. Fits most sinks. Made from food-grade silicone and stainless steel. Heat-resistant, can be used as trivet. Easy to clean and store.

Adjustable laptop stand with 6 height levels. Improves posture and reduces neck strain. Aluminum alloy construction. Ventilated design prevents overheating. Foldable and portable. Fits laptops 10-17 inches.

Acupressure mat and pillow set for pain relief and relaxation. Stimulates pressure points to reduce tension. Eco-friendly materials. Includes carrying bag. Helps with back pain, stress, and sleep quality.

Professional 15-piece knife set with wooden block. High-carbon stainless steel blades. Ergonomic handles. Includes chef knife, bread knife, utility knives, steak knives, and kitchen shears. Hand wash recommended.

Resistance tube set with 5 tubes of varying resistance. Includes handles, door anchor, and ankle straps. Stackable up to 150 lbs resistance. Portable and versatile. Great for strength training and rehabilitation.
Adjustable phone stand with sturdy aluminum base. Compatible with all phones and small tablets. Adjustable height and angle. Non-slip silicone pads. Perfect for desk, kitchen, or bedside table.
High-potency probiotic supplement with 60 billion CFU and 10 strains. Supports digestive health and immune function. Delayed-release capsules. Shelf-stable, no refrigeration needed. 30-day supply.
Non-stick silicone baking mats, 2-pack. Fits half-sheet pans. Reusable and eco-friendly alternative to parchment paper. Heat-resistant up to 480°F. Dishwasher safe. Makes cleanup easy.
Heavy-duty wall-mounted pull-up bar. Supports up to 440 lbs. Multiple grip positions. Sturdy steel construction with foam padding. Includes all mounting hardware. Space-saving home gym equipment.

Fast wireless charging pad compatible with all Qi-enabled devices. 10W fast charging for compatible phones. LED indicator light. Slim design with non-slip surface. Includes USB cable. Case-friendly up to 5mm.
Vitamin D3 (cholecalciferol) 5000 IU softgels. Supports bone health and immune function. Easy-to-swallow softgels. Non-GMO and gluten-free. 360-day supply (1 per day).

Multi-functional pressure cooker, 6-quart capacity. 7-in-1: pressure cooker, slow cooker, rice cooker, steamer, sauté, yogurt maker, and warmer. Digital controls with 13 programs. Stainless steel pot. Includes recipe book.

Wooden balance board for core strength and stability training. Anti-slip surface. Durable construction supports up to 350 lbs. Great for surfing, skateboarding, snowboarding practice, or physical therapy.
4K HDMI cables, 2-pack (6ft each). Supports 4K@60Hz, HDR, and Ethernet. Gold-plated connectors. Durable braided cable. Compatible with all HDMI devices. High-speed transmission.
Turmeric curcumin supplement with BioPerine (black pepper extract) for enhanced absorption. Supports joint health and inflammation response. 95% curcuminoids. Vegan capsules. 90-day supply.
Glass food storage containers with locking lids, 10-piece set (5 containers + 5 lids). BPA-free lids. Microwave, oven, freezer, and dishwasher safe (remove lids for oven). Airtight and leak-proof.
Ab roller wheel with knee pad. Ergonomic handles with non-slip grip. Stable dual wheels. Targets abs, arms, and back. Portable and easy to use. Great for home workouts.
Mesh desk organizer with 5 compartments and 1 drawer. Keeps office supplies organized. Sturdy metal construction. Space-saving design. Modern black finish. Perfect for home or office.
Wired earphones with passive noise isolation. Premium sound quality. Built-in microphone and remote control. 3.5mm jack compatible with most devices. Tangle-free cable. Includes 3 ear tip sizes.
Apple cider vinegar gummies with the mother. Supports digestion and weight management. Great-tasting apple flavor. Vegan and gluten-free. 60-day supply.
Immersion hand blender with 500W motor. Variable speed control. Includes whisk and milk frother attachments. Stainless steel blades. Ergonomic grip. Perfect for soups, smoothies, and sauces.
Adjustable ankle weights, 5 lbs each (10 lbs total). Removable weight pockets. Secure Velcro closure. Comfortable neoprene material. Adds intensity to workouts, walking, or physical therapy.
Blue light blocking glasses for computer use. Reduces eye strain and improves sleep. Clear lenses with anti-glare coating. Lightweight frame. Available in multiple styles. Includes protective case.

1080p Full HD webcam with built-in microphone. Auto-focus and light correction. 90-degree wide angle lens. USB plug-and-play. Compatible with Windows, Mac, and Linux. Perfect for video calls and streaming.
Fish oil omega-3 supplement, 1000mg per softgel. EPA and DHA for heart and brain health. Molecularly distilled for purity. Lemon flavor to reduce fishy aftertaste. 180-day supply.
Stainless steel measuring cups and spoons set. Includes 5 cups and 5 spoons with engraved measurements. Stackable for easy storage. Ring to keep set together. Dishwasher safe.
Textured medicine ball, 10 lbs. Durable rubber construction. Easy-grip surface. Versatile for strength training, core workouts, and rehab. Bounces for added exercise variety.
High-capacity power bank 20000mAh. Charges phones 4-6 times. Dual USB outputs for charging 2 devices simultaneously. LED battery indicator. Fast charging input and output. Includes USB cable.
Magnesium glycinate supplement, 400mg per serving. Highly absorbable form. Supports muscle relaxation, sleep, and stress relief. Non-GMO and vegan. 120-day supply.
Stainless steel slotted spoon with comfortable handle. Heat-resistant up to 450°F. Dishwasher safe. Sturdy construction. Hanging loop for convenient storage. Essential kitchen utensil.

Agility training ladder, 15 feet with 12 rungs. Adjustable rungs for customizable spacing. Durable flat rungs won't tangle or flip. Includes carrying bag. Great for football, soccer, basketball training.

Adjustable tablet stand compatible with 4-13 inch tablets and phones. 270-degree rotation. Sturdy aluminum construction. Non-slip base and holder. Folds flat for travel. Perfect for desk, kitchen, or bedside.
Biotin supplement 10000mcg for hair, skin, and nail health. Supports hair growth and strength. Non-GMO and gluten-free. 300-day supply (1 per day).
Stainless steel garlic press with ergonomic handles. Large chamber minces multiple cloves at once. Easy to clean with included cleaning tool. Dishwasher safe. Durable construction.
Suspension trainer straps for bodyweight exercises. Adjustable length. Supports up to 400 lbs. Includes door anchor and workout guide. Portable and versatile. Full-body workout anywhere.

Wireless keyboard and mouse combo with 2.4GHz connection. Full-size keyboard with number pad. Ergonomic mouse design. Long battery life (up to 24 months). Works with Windows and Mac. Includes nano USB receiver.
Melatonin supplement 10mg for sleep support. Drug-free sleep aid. Helps regulate sleep-wake cycle. Berry flavor dissolves under tongue. Vegan and non-habit forming. 120-day supply.
Silicone spatula set, 5 pieces in different sizes. Heat-resistant up to 480°F. Non-stick safe. Stainless steel core for rigidity. Hanging loops. Dishwasher safe. Assorted colors.
Push-up bars with ergonomic foam grips. Sturdy steel construction. Non-slip base. Reduces wrist strain during push-ups. Compact and portable. Supports up to 300 lbs.
USB 3.0 hub with 4 ports. Super-speed data transfer up to 5Gbps. Compact and portable design. LED indicator lights. Compatible with Windows, Mac, and Linux. Includes USB cable.
Organic ashwagandha root extract 1300mg. Supports stress relief and mood. Adaptogenic herb. Black pepper extract for absorption. Vegan capsules. 90-day supply.
Heat-resistant oven mitts and pot holders set, 4 pieces. Protects hands up to 500°F. Non-slip silicone grip. Machine washable. Hanging loops. Modern design in multiple colors.
Heavy battle rope, 30 feet long and 1.5 inches thick. Durable poly dacron construction. Excellent for cardio and full-body conditioning. Includes anchor strap. Weight approximately 15 lbs.
Monitor stand riser with storage drawer. Raises monitor to ergonomic height. Sturdy metal mesh construction. Drawer for office supplies. Supports up to 44 lbs. Dimensions: 16x9x5 inches.
Elderberry gummies for immune support. With vitamin C and zinc. Delicious berry flavor. Pectin-based, gelatin-free. Supports immune health year-round. 60-day supply.
Wine opener set with corkscrew, foil cutter, and wine stopper. Ergonomic double-hinged design. Stainless steel construction. Includes wooden storage box. Perfect gift for wine lovers.
Slam ball 20 lbs with textured surface. Durable rubber shell doesn't bounce. Ideal for high-intensity workouts, CrossFit, and functional training. Available in multiple weights.
Portable SSD external hard drive 1TB. USB 3.1 Gen 2 for ultra-fast data transfer. Compact and durable aluminum design. Compatible with Windows, Mac, and gaming consoles. Includes USB-C cable.
CoQ10 ubiquinol 200mg, the active form. Supports heart health and cellular energy. Enhanced absorption. Soy-free softgels. 60-day supply.
Wooden spoon set, 6 pieces in different sizes. Made from natural bamboo. Won't scratch non-stick cookware. Heat-resistant and durable. Hand wash recommended.
Speed jump rope with ball bearing handles. Adjustable cable length up to 10 feet. Aluminum handles. Ideal for double-unders and cardio workouts. Includes spare cable.
10-inch LED ring light with adjustable tripod stand (up to 62 inches). 3 color modes and 10 brightness levels. Phone holder included. Perfect for photography, makeup, streaming, and video calls.
Zinc supplement 50mg for immune support. Supports immune function and skin health. Easy-to-swallow tablets. Non-GMO and gluten-free. 250-day supply.
Manual citrus juicer for lemons, limes, and oranges. Sturdy stainless steel construction. Non-slip base. Dishwasher safe. Extracts maximum juice with minimal effort. Easy to use and clean.
Cast iron kettlebell 25 lbs. Smooth finish with wide handle. Versatile for swings, squats, and Turkish get-ups. Durable construction. Color-coded by weight. Build strength and endurance.
External hard drive 2TB with USB 3.0. Fast data transfer speeds. Compact and portable design. Plug-and-play compatible with Windows and Mac. Includes USB cable and backup software.
B-complex vitamin supplement with all 8 B vitamins. Supports energy metabolism and nervous system. Vegan capsules. Non-GMO. 120-day supply.
Large salad spinner with 5-quart capacity. Easy pump mechanism. BPA-free plastic. Non-slip base. Locks for compact storage. Doubles as serving bowl. Dishwasher safe.
Wooden plyo box for box jumps and step-ups. 3-in-1 design with heights 20, 18, and 16 inches. Sturdy construction supports up to 350 lbs. Non-slip surface. Great for CrossFit and functional training.

Wireless presenter with laser pointer. 2.4GHz connection up to 100 feet. Intuitive controls for PowerPoint. USB receiver stores in presenter. Includes carrying pouch. Perfect for teachers and professionals.
Probiotics specifically formulated for women's health. 50 billion CFU with 16 strains. Supports digestive, immune, and vaginal health. Delayed-release capsules. 30-day supply.
Bamboo bread box with roll-top lid. Keeps bread fresh longer. Natural ventilation prevents mold. Eco-friendly material. Compact design fits on countertop. Easy to clean.

Vibrating foam roller with 3 speed settings. High-intensity vibrations enhance muscle recovery. Rechargeable battery lasts up to 2 hours. Textured surface. Includes carry case. Great for post-workout recovery.
